            "participant": {
                "name": "default",
                "line": {
                    "soundtoplay": "voice/beast/1_SANCTUARY1_081_010",
                    "text": "%BEAST%: Storm, I have been quite anxious to hear your impressions of this rather bizarre pairing.",
                    "response": {
                        "text": "%BLANK%",
                        "line": {
                            "soundtoplay": "voice/storm/1_SANCTUARY1_081_011",
                            "text": "%STORM%: I certainly never would have predicted it, but we owe Magneto.",
                            "response": {
                                "text": "%BLANK%",
                                "line": {
                                    "soundtoplay": "voice/beast/1_SANCTUARY1_081_012",
                                    "text": "%BEAST%: But I would wager the X-Men would have aided the Genoshans even without the rescue of Charles.",
                                    "response": {
                                        "text": "%BLANK%",
                                        "line": {
                                            "soundtoplay": "voice/storm/1_SANCTUARY1_081_013",
                                            "text": "%STORM%: But I wonder if our two teams will last very long together. Both sides are constantly on the verge of fighting.",
                                            "response": {
                                                "text": "%BLANK%",
                                                "line": {
                                                    "soundtoplay": "voice/beast/1_SANCTUARY1_081_014",
                                                    "text": "%BEAST%: This is a very tenuous alliance.",
                                                    "response": {
                                                        "text": "%BLANK%",
                                                        "line": {
                                                            "soundtoplay": "voice/storm/1_SANCTUARY1_081_015",
                                                            "text": "%STORM%: You don't suppose this is all some sort of elaborate trap that Magneto has set for us, do you?",
                                                            "response": {
                                                                "text": "%BLANK%",
                                                                "line": {
                                                                    "soundtoplay": "voice/beast/1_SANCTUARY1_081_016",
                                                                    "text": "%BEAST%: I've had that nagging suspicion, but I don't believe it's truly the case.",
                                                                    "response": {
                                                                        "text": "%BLANK%",
                                                                        "line": {
                                                                            "soundtoplay": "voice/storm/1_SANCTUARY1_081_017",
                                                                            "text": "%STORM%: But that's not to say Magneto wouldn't take the opportunity to hurt the X-Men if presented the chance.",
                                                                            "response": {
                                                                                "text": "%BLANK%",
                                                                                "line": {
                                                                                    "soundtoplay": "voice/beast/1_SANCTUARY1_081_018",
                                                                                    "text": "%BEAST%: Oh yes. There's always that possibility, Ororo. We'll just have to remain constantly vigilant.",
                                                                                    "response": {
                                                                                        "tagjump": "autogen_tag_1",
                                                                                        "text": "%END%"
                                                                                    }
                                                                                }
                                                                            }
                                                                        }
                                                                    }
                                                                }
                                                            }
                                                        }
                                                    }
                                                }
                                            }
                                        }
                                    }
                                }
                            }
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        },
        "startCondition": {
            "participant": {
                "name": "default",
                "line": {
                    "soundtoplay": "voice/beast/1_sanctuary1_080_030",
                    "soundtoplayb": "voice/beast/1_sanctuary1_080_040",
                    "text": "%Beast%: Greetings again, my friend. How may I be of assistance?",
